ext-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3. 在进行自动备份的时候，往往需要需要产生的日志自动增加备份的日期</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">export Today=`date +%Y%m%d` </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">rman target /&nbsp;&nbsp; log /usr/oracle/${Today}.log</span></span></p>\n','Rman登录及日志记录',92,'CJVerify'),(56,'2020-10-30 08:59:42',0,'2020-10-30 09:01:14','','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-sql\">SQL&gt; create user myuser_rmanBK identified by 123456;\n\nUser created\n\n\nSQL&gt; grant sysdba to myuser_rmanBK;\n\nGrant succeeded\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">查看</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-sql\">SQL&gt;  select * from v$pwfile_users;</code></pre>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','创建Rman用户',92,'CJVerify'),(57,'2020-10-30 09:03:11',0,'2020-10-30 09:03:11','sysdba、sysoper，V$PWFILE_USERS','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>V$PWFILE_USERS 列出的是password文件里已授予sysdba、sysoper权限的用户，</p>\n\n<p>如果查询没有记录，那就有可能没有了password文件了，</p>\n\n<p>没有了密码文件当然sqlplus sys/xx as sysdba这种用sys用sysdba用户就无法登录了。</p>\n','权限-特殊权限',87,'CJVerify'),(58,'2020-10-30 09:12:12',0,'2020-10-30 09:12:12','','<h2><span style=\"color:#c0392b\"><strong>1.查看配置</strong></span></h2>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-sql\">RMAN&gt; show all;</code></pre>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#c0392b\"><strong>1.更改Rman默认配置</strong></span></h2>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.保留策略 窗口-7天</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<pre>\n<code>RMAN&gt; configure retention policy to recovery window of 7 days;</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.打开备份优化</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<pre>\n<code>RMAN&gt;  configure backup optimization on;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3.控制文件、参数文件自动备份</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<pre>\n<code>RMAN&gt;  configure controlfile autobackup on;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">4.设置并行级别为2<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><a href=\"#_msocom_1\" id=\"_anchor_1\" name=\"_msoanchor_1\">[M1]</a>&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></h4>\n\n<pre>\n<code>RMAN&gt; configure device type disk parallelism  2;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">5.设置加密及加密密码、加密算法</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">暂时不设置加密</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">6.配置归档日志保留策略</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认情况下，oracle将配置的备份保留策略应用于归档重做日志</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认情况下，归档日志删除策略设置为none，需要手动执行归档日志的删除</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"background-color:lime\">如果是指为none(默认)，使用Rman的备份保留策略？？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">单独配置的删除策略对FRA及之外的归档重做日志有效</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FRA中的oracle会尽量保存，除非空间不允许，由oracle自动删除</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FRA之外的需要手动删除:delete obsolete&nbsp; ;&nbsp; delete archivelog</span></span></p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">1.如果配置DG则如下配置</span></span></h5>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; configure archivelog deletion policy to applied on standby;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><strong>此配置启用DG后可用。当归档日志应用于备用数据库后将其标志为删除。Oracle会将其从FRA中删除</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">2.否则如下配置</span></span></h5>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">（默认情况，无需更改）</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; configure archivelog deletion policy to none;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">继承默认的保留策略</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">10.最终的默认配置</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; show all;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">db_unique_name 为 SORDB 的数据库的 RMAN 配置参数为:</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE RETENTION POLICY TO RECOVERY WINDOW OF 7 DAYS;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE BACKUP OPTIMIZATION ON;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DEFAULT DEVICE TYPE TO DISK; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE CONTROLFILE AUTOBACKUP ON;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE CONTROLFILE AUTOBACKUP FORMAT FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO &#39;%F&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DEVICE TYPE DISK PARALLELISM 2 BACKUP TYPE TO BACKUPSET;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DATAFILE BACKUP COPIES FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO 1; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ARCHIVELOG BACKUP COPIES FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO 1; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE MAXSETSIZE TO UNLIMITED; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ENCRYPTION FOR DATABASE OFF; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ENCRYPTION ALGORITHM &#39;AES128&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE COMPRESSION ALGORITHM &#39;BASIC&#39; AS OF RELEASE &#39;DEFAULT&#39; OPTIMIZE FOR LOAD TRUE ; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ARCHIVELOG DELETION POLICY TO NONE;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE SNAPSHOT CONTROLFILE NAME TO &#39;E:\\APP\\ADMINISTRATOR\\PRODUCT\\11.2.0\\DBHOME_1\\DATABASE\\SNCFSORDB.ORA&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"msocomtxt\" id=\"_com_1\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n','Rman配置查看及修改',92,'CJVerify'),(59,'2020-10-30 09:20:25',0,'2020-10-30 09:50:38','','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.使用默认配置执行完全备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; backup database plus archivelog delete all input;</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">2.使用run块执行level0的增量备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code>run{\nallocate channel c1 type disk;\nallocate channel c2 type disk;\nallocate channel c3 type disk;\nbackup as compressed backupset incremental level 0 database plus archivelog delete all input;\ncrosscheck backup;\ndelete noprompt expired backup;\nreport obsolete;\ndelete noprompt obsolete;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">3.使用run块执行level1的增量备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code>run{\ndelete noprompt obsolete;\nallocate channel c1 type disk;\nallocate channel c2 type disk;\nallocate channel c3 type disk;\nallocate channel c4 type disk;\nbackup as compressed backupset incremental level 1 database;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">4.Windows/Linux自动执行Rman备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<div>\n<div class=\"msocomtxt\" id=\"_com_1\">\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#e67e22\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\">$ crontab -l</span></span></strong></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">0 1 * * 0,4 sh /home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman0.sh</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">0 1 * * 1,2,3,5,6 sh /home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman1.sh</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"msocomtxt\"><span style=\"color:#e67e22\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\">$ cat /home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman0.sh</span></span></strong></span></span></h5>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">#!/bin/bash\n\nsource /home/oracle/.bash_profile\n\n$ORACLE_HOME/bin/rman target / nocatalog cmdfile=/home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman0 log=/home/oracle/rmantask/log/backup0.log</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"msocomtxt\"><span style=\"color:#e67e22\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\">$ cat /home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman1.sh</span></span></strong></span></span></h5>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">if [ -f ~/.bash_profile ];\n\nthen\n\n. ~/.bash_profile\n\nfi\n\nrman target / cmdfile=/home/oracle/rmantask/bin/rman1 log=/home/oracle/rmantask/log/backup1.log</code></pre>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n','执行Rman备份',92,'CJVerify'),(60,'2020-10-30 09:30:49',0,'2020-10-30 11:19:46','','<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.plus archivelog</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">备份归档日志</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.delete all input</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">在备份的同时删除已备份的归档日志</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3. delete noprompt obsolete</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">run块中的命令</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">可选</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">删除过时备份</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">4. backup validate check logical database;</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">run块中命令</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">使用Rman来扫描数据库的物理和逻辑错误</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">此命令不执行备份操作，使用Rman来扫描数据库的物理和逻辑错误</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认情况下，Rman会自动检查数据库块的逻辑损坏</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">4.其他可选参数</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">a.include current controfile</span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 迫使Rman将控制文件加入数据库的<strong><u>每个</u></strong>备份集中</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果rman的默认配置执行了控制文件自动备份，那么还会将控制文件存储在另一个单独的备份文件中，这样就会有2个控制文件的备份</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><span style=\"background-color:lime\">在Archivelog模式中，这2个控制文件稍有不同</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">b.多段备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">待备份的文件划分为多个文件块（将文件逻辑的划分成连续块）</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">Rman将创建多个备份集，每个文件段使用一个备份集</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">c. 压缩</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.Null数据库块压缩</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.Rman备份压缩</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认压缩、低级压缩、中级压缩、高级压缩</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">非默认压缩需要购买许可</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">测试</span></span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">d.标记 和 还原点</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">标记对应特定备份</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">还原点对应特定时间</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">e.限定备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">限定时间</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">可设置为在限定时间内无法完成依旧不报错</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">备份优先级：较早备份的数据文件具有较高的优先级，可以提前备份</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">f.限定备份集的大小</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">g. 跳过脱机的、不可访问的、只读的数据文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">h. 强制备份只读的数据文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 即使启用了备份优化，也会强制执行备份只读数据文件</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">i.基于上次备份的时间来备份数据文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">1.只备份新添加的数据文件</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">2.备份指定时间内没有备份的数据文件</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">j. Rman赋值的设备上生成副本备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:lime\">一个位置，多个备份，有何作用？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','Rman备份命令参数解析',109,'CJVerify'),(61,'2020-10-30 09:43:04',0,'2020-10-30 09:51:49','crosscheck，report obsolete ，noprompt','<p><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">EXPIRED状态</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>此状态与crosscheck命令相关，crosscheck backup 命令是对备份进行交叉检查，检查备份集是否有效。</p>\n\n<p>当crosscheck命令检查到某备份已经在系统层面删除的时候即物理上不存在的时候，就会将available状态置为expired状态，</p>\n\n<p>但这个时候并没有真正删除备份【所以删除备份不能在系统层面删除，而应该在rman中删除，使用delete backup】；</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">OBSOLETE状态：</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>obsolete状态是根据rman备份的保留策略来定的，当超过保留策略的备份就会被标记为obsolete状态，<br />\n使用 report obsolete 命令来查看，<br />\n使用delete noprompt obselete来删除备份；</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">参数</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">noprompt</span></span></h5>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">避免删除时弹出验证窗口</span></span></p>\n','EXPIRED状态和OBSOLETE状态',94,'CJVerify'),(62,'2020-10-30 09:55:02',0,'2020-10-30 09:58:02','','<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#ed7d31\">&nbsp;corsscheck 交叉校验RMAN备份</span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">查看备份集、备份集片、副本的状态</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><strong><u>判断是否存储在备份介质上</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">crosscheck会将过时备份标记位Expiered</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8089/cjCKEditor/downloader/image/48\" style=\"height:166px; width:554px\" /></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">crosscheck状态</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">Available, Expired</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">v$backup_set 备份集片</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">v$datafile_copy 副本备份</span></span></span></h3>\n',' corsscheck-Basic',97,'CJImproved'),(63,'2020-10-30 09:56:37',0,'2020-10-30 09:56:37','','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">对备份集进行验证，确保这个备份集能够被还原</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">一般情况下，在生产环境中，完成备份后会使用backp validate check logical命令进行数据库验证</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">validate一般用于特殊情况：检查特定的备份集或在FRA中检查所有的备份集</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">validate默认只检查物理损坏，如果需要检查逻辑损坏，需要check logical参数</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">validate无法查出某些损坏类型：例如块与块之间的损坏问题</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">实测</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.测试backupset</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">91为backupset的 BS关键字</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; validate backupset 91;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 或者</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; validate check logical backupset 91;</span></span></p>\n','Validate 备份验证',96,'CJImproved'),(64,'2020-10-30 09:59:27',0,'2020-10-30 09:59:27','','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">冗余策略的实施不会从Rman目录中删除备份，只是将这些备份标记为过时（Obsolete）状态。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">包含keep参数的change命令</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">使用这个命令，被修改的备份会被认为是一个长期备份（<strong><u>Long-Term Backup</u></strong>），不受相应的保留策略影响</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如果使用闪回恢复区，就不可以使用keep命令的keep forever字句</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><strong><u>这个命令需要有恢复目录的支持</u></strong></span></span></p>\n','Rman冗余策略',94,'CJImproved'),(65,'2020-10-30 10:02:45',0,'2020-10-30 10:02:45','','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.unavailable状态</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">在恢复和还原期间，不会考虑unavailable状态的备份，在执行delete expired期间，这些备份记录不会被删除</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">2.带delete参数的change命令</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">物理删除备份集，并从控制文件和恢复目录中删除</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如果使用FRA,只有当FRA中其他文件被删除时才会删除该物理文件</span></span></p>\n',' change 修改备份状态',99,'CJImproved'),(66,'2020-10-30 10:05:02',0,'2020-10-30 10:05:02','','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">判断数据库当前的可恢复状态，提供数据库备份的特定信息</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.最近n天未备份的数据文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">2冗余或者恢复窗口</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">3.报告过时的备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">report obsolete</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">4.报告数据库模式schema</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">5.报告数据库的不可恢复操作</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">Rman是否备份了闪回日志？？？</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n','Report',100,'CJImproved'),(67,'2020-10-30 10:06:02',0,'2020-10-30 10:06:02','','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">在数据库控制文件或者恢复目录中查询备份历史记录</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">包含了数据库中对应到列表的备份集和归档日志备份列表</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.list backup summary</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; list backup summary;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</