mily:等线\">闪回日志</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">重做日志</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">Rman数据文件</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">闪回日志？？</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">除了FRA还要在其他磁盘、其他服务器进行备份！！！！</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如何为每个数据库单独分配可用的配额</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.0.3 为Rman单独创建一个数据库用户</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 权限？tablespace?</span></span></p>\n','Rman配置-基础配置',104,'CJImproved'),(72,'2020-10-30 10:58:08',0,'2020-10-30 10:58:08','','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.1.2基础</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">设置控制文件中保存备份记录的时间</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认值为7天</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:28px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">改参数直接影响数据库控制文件的大小，备份记录会不断保存在控制文件中</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.1.1建议</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><u>改参数的值大于等于数据库备份保存的周期值</u></strong>，否则可能备份文件存在但是在控制文件中不存在记录</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 强烈建议使用恢复目录，并将保存在控制文件中的记录数量控制在30-60天</span></span></p>\n',' CONTROL_FILE_RECORD_KEEP_TIME',105,'CJVerify'),(73,'2020-10-30 11:13:28',0,'2020-10-30 11:14:58','','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">查看默认配置</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">RMAN&gt; show all;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">使用目标数据库控制文件替代恢复目录</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">db_unique_name 为 CJOR 的数据库的 RMAN 配置参数为:</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">--</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">保留策略</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE RETENTION POLICY TO REDUNDANCY 1; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">默认值为关闭，如果打开，rman将对备份的数据文件及归档等文件进行一种优化的算法。</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE BACKUP OPTIMIZATION OFF; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">是指定所有I/O操作的设备类型是硬盘或者磁带，默认值是硬盘</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DEFAULT DEVICE TYPE TO DISK; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">控制文件自动备份??</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE CONTROLFILE AUTOBACKUP OFF; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">控制文件备份格式及路径</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE CONTROLFILE AUTOBACKUP FORMAT FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO &#39;%F&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">配置并行度</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DEVICE TYPE DISK PARALLELISM 1 BACKUP TYPE TO BACKUPSET; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">是配置数据库的每次备份的copy数量，oracle的每一次备份都可以有多份完全相同的拷贝。</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE DATAFILE BACKUP COPIES FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO 1; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">是设置数据库的归档日志的存放设备类型</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ARCHIVELOG BACKUP COPIES FOR DEVICE TYPE DISK TO 1; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">备份集大小 maxsetsize</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE MAXSETSIZE TO UNLIMITED; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">这个参数是配置数据库备份加密的，从10G后开始有，防止备份的文件被异地还原泄露数据</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ENCRYPTION FOR DATABASE OFF; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">对加密算法的配置，同上也是备份加密设置有关的，对这两个参数相关的设置可以参考盖国强的一篇文章：http://www.eygle.com/digest/2008/12/oracle_database_10g_11g_rman.html</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ENCRYPTION ALGORITHM &#39;AES128&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">备份压缩相关的功能，这个使用的是基本的压缩算法</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE COMPRESSION ALGORITHM &#39;BASIC&#39; AS OF RELEASE &#39;DEFAULT&#39; OPTIMIZE FOR LOAD TRUE ; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">归档日志的保留策略</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE ARCHIVELOG DELETION POLICY TO NONE; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">--</span><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">控制文件快照的位置</span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE SNAPSHOT CONTROLFILE NAME TO &#39;D:\\ORACLESERVER\\PRODUCT\\11.2.0\\DBHOME_1\\DATABASE\\SNCFCJOR.ORA&#39;; # default</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">v$rman_configuration</span></span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">查看非默认的Rman配置</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\"><span style=\"color:navy\">select * from v$rman_configuration;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.1 信道配置</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">信道与备份集</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">通常每个信道创建一个备份集</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">可以创建多个</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.配置设备类型device type</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.配置backup type</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; backupset</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">coompressed backupset</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; copy</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3.配置信道数=并行级别<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><a href=\"#_msocom_1\" id=\"_anchor_1\" name=\"_msoanchor_1\">[M1]</a>&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">prallelism</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如果有多个cpu，但只有一个存储位置（通道），仍旧可以通过启用并行机制利用多通道功能。如果分配的通道数量超过了并行度的设置，RMAN仅会向与并行度匹配的通道写入数据，并且会忽略超出并行度的其他通道。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如何决定并行级别？？？有何参照、、</span></span></h5>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">4.手动和自动分配</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">5.其他参数</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">maxpiecesize</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">maxopenfiles</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">rate</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.2 备份集、备份集片</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.设置备份及大小</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2. 排除某些tablespace</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3. 备份集名称</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果使用FRA,Oracle将会基于<strong><span style=\"background-color:lime\">OMF</span><span style=\"background-color:lime\">命名标准</span></strong>创建备份集的文件名称</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果使用format参数：一般使用%U关键字，此关键字会创建唯一的名称</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">4.备份集与备份集片</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">备份集是逻辑概念</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">备份集片是实际的物理文件</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">每个备份集关联一个或多个备份片</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.3安全连接--口令文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.配置oracle使用口令文件</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">1.如何判断当前oracle使用那个参数文件</span></span></h5>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">2.如何配置数据库使用某个具体的口令文件</span></span></h5>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.4 备份优化</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><a name=\"_Hlk535839946\">RMAN&gt; configure backup optimization on;</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">新的 RMAN 配置参数:</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">CONFIGURE BACKUP OPTIMIZATION ON;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">已成功存储新的 RMAN 配置参数</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">备份优化：使Rman默认不备份没有发生变化的表空间</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.5格式串 format</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当备份到FRA时，不建议使用格式串</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; format参数顶一个备份片放入磁盘的位置以及备份片的命名约定</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如果不设置，备份到FRA中的备份文件使用OMF命名规则</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.6还原配置</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.7 快照配置文件设置</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.8 控制文件和数据库参数文件的自动备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.设置备份时自动备份控制文件和参数文件</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><a name=\"_Hlk535840196\">RMAN&gt; configure controlfile autobackup on;</a></span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2. 当控制文件变化时，自动备份控制文件(可选)</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.9 保留策略</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.基于窗口的保留策略</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 实际上，备份存在的时间比定义的时间更长</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; rman会保留到最近完全备份或者0级增量备份</span></span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.基于冗余的保留策略</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3.无保留策略</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.10 加密级别</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.透明模式</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">2.口令模式</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">3.双重模式</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">透明模式和口令模式</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.10-2 加密算法</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2.10 归档日志删除策略</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认情况下，oracle将配置的备份保留策略应用于归档重做日志</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">默认情况下，归档日志删除策略设置为none，需要手动执行归档日志的删除</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"background-color:lime\">如果是指为none(默认)，使用Rman的备份保留策略？？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">单独配置的删除策略对FRA及之外的归档重做日志有效</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FRA中的oracle会尽量保存，除非空间不允许，由oracle自动删除</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FRA之外的需要手动删除:delete obsolete&nbsp; ;&nbsp; delete archivelog</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8089/cjCKEditor/downloader/image/49\" style=\"height:279px; width:554px\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">为什么会跳过归档日志</span></span><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">备份？？？？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<div>\n<hr />\n<div>\n<div class=\"msocomtxt\" id=\"_com_1\"><a name=\"_msocom_1\"></a>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;<a href=\"#_msoanchor_1\">[M1]</a>不同信道需要不同的磁盘控制器？？</span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n','Rman默认配置',106,'CJVerify'),(74,'2020-10-30 11:16:14',0,'2020-10-30 11:16:14','','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.联机重做日志、控制文件</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#00b050\">1.1OMF的DB_CREATE_ONLINE_LOG_DEST_n</span></span></span></h4>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">a.</span><span style=\"background-color:lime\">如果配置了OMF的DB_CREATE_ONLINE_LOG_DEST_n(联机重做日志配置)</span></span></span></h5>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"background-color:lime\">则使用alter database add logfile和alter database add standby logfile来创建FRA中的联机重做日志</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">如果创建此参数，将在这些位置创建控制文件和联机重做日志文件，即便此时创建了FRA,也不会在FRA中创建文件</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n\n<h5 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">b.如果没有配置了OMF的DB_CREATE_ONLINE_LOG_DEST_n</span></span></h5>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"background-color:lime\">CREATE_FILE_DEST</span><span style=\"background-color:lime\">和DB_RECOVERY_FILE_DEST参数定义的位置都会创建控制文件和联机重做日志文件</span></span></span></p>\n','FRA--联机重做日志、控制文件',108,'CJImproved'),(75,'2020-10-30 11:21:28',0,'2020-10-30 11:21:28','','<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;等线 Light&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#ed7d31\">基础流程</span></span></span></h2>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.1日志切换操作</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.2 备份现存所有归档日志</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.3-1数据库备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.3-2 日志切换操作</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.3-3备份剩余的归档重做日志</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"color:#00b0f0\">1.4 控制文件和参数文件备份</span></span></span></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-sql\">RMAN&gt; backup database plus archivelog;</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">2019-02-23 09:26:57.601000 +08:00</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"background-color:aqua\">ALTER SYSTEM ARCHIVE LOG</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">Thread 1 advanced to log sequence 24 (LGWR switch)</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp; Current log# 3 seq# 24 mem# 0: E:\\APP\\ADMINISTRATOR\\ORADATA\\SORDB\\REDO03.LOG</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">&nbsp; Current log# 3 seq# 24 mem# 1: G:\\ORACLE_FRA_AREA\\MYREDO03.LOG</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style