>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>配置</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>说明</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"44\">\n<p>1</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>Inspur#<strong>config</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>进入全局配置模式。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"44\">\n<p>2</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>Inspur(config)#dhcp-snooping</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>使能全局DHCP Snooping功能。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"44\">\n<p>3</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>Inspur(config)#<strong>interface</strong> <em>interface-type interface-number</em></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>进入物理层接口配置模式。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"44\">\n<p>4</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>Inspur(config-gigaethernet1/1/1)#dhcp-snooping</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>使能接口的DHCP Snooping功能。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"44\">\n<p>5</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"315\">\n<p>Inspur(config-gigaethernet1/1/1)#<strong>dhcp- snooping trust</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"276\">\n<p>配置DHCP Snooping信任接口。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>查看命令</p>\n<table width=\"527\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"281\">\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;参数</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"246\">\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;描述</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"281\">\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; show dhcp-snooping</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"246\">\n<p>显示当前的dhcp-snooping配置信息。</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table width=\"527\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"294\">\n<p>命令</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"233\">\n<p>描述</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"294\">\n<p>&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;show dhcp-snooping interfaces GigabitEthernet 0/x</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-color: #34495e; border-style: solid;\" width=\"233\">\n<p>显示 &nbsp;dhcp snooping 信息</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>示例：</p>\n<p>dingyunkai# config terminal&nbsp; 进入全局模式</p>\n<p>dingyunkai(config)# dhcp-snooping 全局使能dhcp-snooping功能</p>\n<p>dingyunkai(config)# interface GigabitEthernet 0/1 进入端口</p>\n<p>dingyunkai(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/1)# dhcp-snooping&nbsp; 使能dhcp-snooping功能</p>\n<p>dingyunkai(config)# interface GigabitEthernet 0/1</p>\n<p>dingyunkai(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/1)# dhcp-snooping trust&nbsp; 将端口设置为信任端口</p>',51,'1','2020-03-05 10:27:18','2020-03-06 16:50:26',51,105),(52,'浪潮6650---学习文档--20200102','浪潮6650基础命令','<p>要求：按拓扑图、IP规划表配置交换机实现PC正常上网</p>\n<p>浪潮：</p>\n<p>缺省配置，则会显示&ldquo;Login:&rdquo;提示符，输入用户名inspur和密码inspur后，进入普通用户模式，在屏幕上显示：</p>\n<p>Inspur#</p>\n<p>特权用户模式下，输入config terminal命令，则可进入全局配置模式。</p>\n<p>Inspur#config</p>\n<p>Inspur(config)#</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>特权用户模式下，输入config terminal命令，则可进入全局配置模式。</p>\n<p>浪潮：特权用户模式</p>\n<p>Inspur#config</p>\n<p>Inspur(config)#</p>\n<p>华为：特权用户模式</p>\n<p>system-view</p>\n<p>&lt;WenHuaZhongXin-CanTing-JiFang&gt;system-view</p>\n<p>System View: return to User View with Ctrl+Z.</p>\n<p>[WenHuaZhongXin-CanTing-JiFang]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Telnet 交换机管理</li>\n</ul>\n<p>实现所有交换机可以远程Telnet 登录,密码设置为123456，</p>\n<p>Telnet设置：</p>\n<p>&nbsp;华为：</p>\n<p>user-interface vty 0 4</p>\n<p>&nbsp;user privilege level 15</p>\n<p>&nbsp;set authentication password cipher 123456</p>\n<p>&nbsp;idle-timeout 3 0</p>\n<p>浪潮：</p>\n<p>line vty 0 4</p>\n<p>&nbsp;privilege level 15</p>\n<p>&nbsp;password 123456</p>\n<p>&nbsp;login</p>\n<p>timeout login response 300</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>VLAN 、IP划分</li>\n</ul>\n<p>通过配置交换机VLAN、IP实现接入办公、监控电脑。</p>\n<p>interface Vlan118</p>\n<p>&nbsp;ip address 172.16.18.241 255.255.255.0</p>\n<p>华为端口：</p>\n<p>interface GigabitEthernet0/0/1</p>\n<p>&nbsp;port link-type access</p>\n<p>&nbsp;port default vlan 118</p>\n<p>浪潮端口：</p>\n<p>interface GigabitEthernet0/48</p>\n<p>&nbsp;switchport mode access</p>\n<p>switchport access vlan 118</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>路由区别：</li>\n</ul>\n<p>华为：ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 172.16.18.254</p>\n<p>浪潮：ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 172.16.18.254</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>保存：</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Inspur#<strong>write&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>保存配置信息。</p>\n<p>或者copy&nbsp;runing-config startup-config</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/65ffa98f35834a6c9358171a20ed9de6.png\" /></p>\n<table width=\"488\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>设备</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>设备名</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>IP</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-01</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test01</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.241</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-02</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test02</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.242</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-03</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test03</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.243</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-04</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test04</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.244</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-05</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test05</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.245</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p>网络中心-浪潮-06</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"185\">\n<p>wlzx-langcao-test06</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"151\">\n<p>172.16.18.246</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',49,'1','2020-03-05 10:39:53','2020-03-05 10:39:53',NULL,107),(53,'dell s4078OS安装方法','dell s4078OS安装方法','<p><img src=\"uploadFile/ebdbb45ef3fb451a9e5ef20c3eee6336.png\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/c8c9a19fa9754321a73fe8e1f698cf06.png\" /></p>\n<p>系统下载地址：OS10 120 天试用期： <a href=\"https://www.force10networks.com/CSPortal20/Software/software/OS10_Enterprise_10.4.3.4.tar\">https://www.force10networks.com/CSPortal20/Software/software/OS10_Enterprise_10.4.3.4.tar</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/b07921836da94eda9fec9d5ddd5792df.png\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Vincent Hua </strong><strong>花志强</strong><br />Senior Technology Service Manager (TSM)<br /><strong>Dell Technologies</strong> | DT Services (AMS)</p>\n<p>mobile <a href=\"tel:+86%2018653178736\">+86 18653178736</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"mailto:Vincent.Hua@Dell.com\">Vincent.Hua@Dell.com</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',49,'1','2020-03-05 10:43:12','2020-03-05 10:43:12',NULL,108),(54,'WA2620i-AGN 刷机及失败恢复添加AC说明','WA2620i-AGN 刷机及失败恢复添加AC说明','<p>注意：</p>\n<p>步骤</p>\n<ul>\n<li>网页刷完后点保存必须重启AP-----直接断电</li>\n<li>重启后再登配置页面删除vlan1 后再重启</li>\n<li>配置AC里如果设备自动发现不能修改，将AC里的自动发现关闭手动添加即可</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>WA2620i-AGN</p>\n<p>一、AC下载固件</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>方法:1 Web升级</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/ba939bdd502849409cad525931a30a4e.png\" /></p>\n<p>1 、AP管理：192.168.0.50</p>\n<p>admin</p>\n<p>h3capadmin</p>\n<p>1、web</p>\n<p>2、重启</p>\n<p>3、CRT</p>\n<p>修改无线VLAN 1</p>\n<p>interface Vlan-interface1</p>\n<p>ip address 192.168.0.50 255.255.255.0</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>ip address dhcp-alloc client-identifier mac Vlan-interface1</p>\n<p>保存重启</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>方法2：Web失败</p>\n<p>======================================================</p>\n<p>|&lt;1&gt; Boot System |</p>\n<p>|&lt;2&gt; Enter Serial SubMenu |</p>\n<p>|&lt;3&gt; Enter Ethernet SubMenu |</p>\n<p>|&lt;4&gt; File Control |</p>\n<p>|&lt;5&gt; Restore to Factory Default Configuration |</p>\n<p>|&lt;6&gt; Skip Current System Configuration |</p>\n<p>|&lt;7&gt; BootWare Operation Menu |</p>\n<p>|&lt;8&gt; Clear Super Password |</p>\n<p>|&lt;9&gt; Storage Device Operation |</p>\n<p>|&lt;0&gt; Reboot |</p>\n<p>============================================================================</p>\n<p>Ctrl+C: Display Copyright</p>\n<p>Ctrl+F: Format File System</p>\n<p>Enter your choice(0-9): 7</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>===================================================</p>\n<p>|Note:the operating device is flash |</p>\n<p>|&lt;1&gt; Backup Full BootWare |</p>\n<p>|&lt;2&gt; Restore Full BootWare |</p>\n<p>|&lt;3&gt; Update BootWare By Serial |</p>\n<p>|&lt;4&gt; Update BootWare By Ethernet |</p>\n<p>|&lt;0&gt; Exit To Main Menu |</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>开机就卡在这只能按Ctrl+D</p>\n<p><br />按Ctrl+D出现<br />=============================================<br />|&lt;1&gt; Modify Serial Interface Parameter |<br />|&lt;2&gt; Update Extend BootWare |<br />|&lt;3&gt; Update Full BootWare |<br />|&lt;4&gt; Boot Extend BootWare |<br />|&lt;5&gt; Boot Backup Extend BootWare |<br />|&lt;0&gt; Reboot |<br />============================