fig)# hostname dingyunkai-s5100交换机命名</p>\n<p>inspur(config)# ip address 172.28.254.120 mask 255.255.255.0 设置交换机管理地址</p>\n<p>inspur(config)# ip default-gateway 172.28.254.254 设置网关</p>\n<p>inspur# vlan 102,116,2000 创建vlan</p>\n<p>inspur(config)# management-vlan vlan 2000 设置管理vlan</p>\n<p>设置上联端口，透传vlan</p>\n<p>inspur(config)# interface GigabitEthernet 0/8&nbsp;</p>\n<p>nspur(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/8)# switch mode trunk&nbsp;</p>\n<p>inspur(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/8)# switch trunk allowed vlan 102,116,2000</p>\n<p>&lt;GigabitEthernet0/8)# no switch trunk allowed vlan 1</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s5100(config)# interface range GigabitEthernet 0/1-0/7 设置端口组</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s5100(config-if-range)# switch mode access&nbsp;</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s5100(config-if-range)# switch access vlan 102</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-S5100(config)# dhcp-snooping</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-S5100(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/8)#dhcp-snooping</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-S5100(config-if-GigabitEthernet0/8)#dhcp-snooping trust</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-S5100(config)# interface range GigabitEthernet 0/1-0/7<br />dingyunkai-S5100(config-if-range)# dhcp-snooping</p>\n<p>开始telnet服务</p>\n<p>inspur(config)# ip telnet</p>\n<p>添加用户</p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s5100(config)# username dingyunkai privilege admin password&nbsp; Dingyunkai123</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">修改初始管理员密码</span></p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s5100(config)# username admin password Dingyunkai123</p>\n<p>Old password: *****</p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s5100#write</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>验证</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/c18ae888293f43adbcd516cb8966de14.png\" /></p>\n<p>配置文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/393e7a784f4d4fc0800c2b6dde82d732.png\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/e865082df24642a399a63ab9dce8de3e.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',51,'1','2020-03-09 