 active&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; console telnet ssh web lan-access&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',51,'1','2020-03-09 10:02:37','2020-03-09 10:02:37',NULL,120),(87,'创建并配置IPv4地址池','创建并配置IPv4地址池','<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config)#ip dhcp server pool 100</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-pool)#$.28.1.1 172.28.1.100 mask 255.255.255.0</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-pool)#dns-server 172.15.254.121</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-pool)#dns-server 172.15.254.122 secondary&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-pool)#gateway 172.28.1.254</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-pool)#gateway 172.28.1.254</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">dingyunkai-s6550(config-gigaethernet1/1/1)#ip dhcp server&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">查看命令</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">Inspur(config)#<strong>show</strong> <strong>ip</strong> <strong>server pool</strong></span></p>',51,'1','2020-03-09 15:00:11','2020-03-09 15:00:11',NULL,120),(88,'配置手工链路聚合',' 配置手工链路聚合','<p>dingyunkai-s6550(config)#interface port-channel 1<br />dingyunkai-s6550(config-port-channel1)#portswitch&nbsp;</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s6550(config-port-channel1)#switchport mode trunk&nbsp;</p>\n<p>设置成功</p>\n<p>dingyunkai-s6550(config-port-channel1)#switchport trunk allowed vlan 1</p>\n<p>本操作会覆盖端口下允许vlan，请输入\'y\'