<tr>\n<td>网线</td>\n<td>　</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>箱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>一、4楼电梯东1室，屋内有网线。（网线上联至东2）无需调整。</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/f0dc0e57bbc44d04a40c100f6675d743.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"923\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/9ea35d9dfe00480aa9bf382fe6fff21c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"677\" height=\"903\" /></p>\n<p>二、4楼电梯东2室内需添加8口交换机一台。用于东2及东1使用。</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/16432a4367994d369bba96baadd69935.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"682\" height=\"909\" /></p>\n<p>三、4楼电梯东梯东3室，目前审计人员在办公，室内有线网络正常。后期改为会议室以供开会使用。可以使用有网线网络无需调整。</p>\n<p>四、4楼电梯东梯东4室大屋，目前室内有8个网线口，后期可能屋内做隔断，需增加交换机2台。</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/efc4596d3dac4bcb8c1c54d09e66b891.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"714\" height=\"952\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/0f30c77af04f4c08bb85d848bec5ac3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"767\" height=\"1023\" /></p>\n<p>五、3楼电梯东1，曹林总经理办公室，室内无网络面板，走明线到达办公桌不美观。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 网线方案，在其办公桌后面的茶水间安装一台无线路由器，供曹林总经理办公室使用。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 茶水间网络通过3楼电梯东2打通隔断进行安装。</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/976959a0ca2b464981e5f3e325aa3b0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"754\" height=\"565\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/1beab106586147a6ab4d94d44eb4e60a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"883\" height=\"662\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/8536380640274b138ebdb9b59aaaf67c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"849\" height=\"1132\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/16fedb60eed040cfad1fa99d9c38de65.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"876\" height=\"1168\" /></p>\n<p>六、其它办公室内都留有网络面板，有线可达。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',49,'1','2020-03-09 16:35:36','2020-03-09 16:35:36',NULL,121),(93,'历史命令','历史命令','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1、显示用户输入的有效历史命令</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>display history-command</strong>&nbsp;[&nbsp;<strong>|&nbsp;</strong>{&nbsp;<strong>begin</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>exclude&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>include&nbsp;</strong>}&nbsp;<em>regular-expression&nbsp;</em>]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"TableText\">访问上一条历史命令上光标键&uarr;或&lt;Ctrl+P&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"TableText\">访问下一条历史命令下光标键&darr;或&lt;Ctrl+N&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"TableText\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">2、配置历史命令缓冲区的大小</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"TableText\"><strong>user-interface</strong>&nbsp;{&nbsp;<em>first-num1</em>&nbsp;[&nbsp;<em>last-num1</em>&nbsp;] | {&nbsp;<strong>aux&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>vty</strong>&nbsp;}&nbsp;<em>first-num2&nbsp;</em>[&nbsp;<em>last-num2&nbsp;</em>] }</p>\n<p class=\"TableText\"><strong>history-command</strong>&nbsp;<strong>max-size</strong>&nbsp;<em>size-value</em></p>\n<p class=\"TableText\">缺省情况下，历史命令缓冲区可存放10条历史命令</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',52,'1','2020-03-09 16:48:47','2020-03-09 16:48:47',NULL,67),(94,'正则表达式过滤显示','正则表达式过滤显示','<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在执行<strong>display</strong>命令查看显示信息时，用户可以使用正则表达式来过滤显示信息，以便快速的找到自己关注的信息。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">过滤显示的使用方法有两种：</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在命令行中通过输入<strong>|&nbsp;</strong>{&nbsp;<strong>begin</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>exclude&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;<strong>include&nbsp;</strong>}&nbsp;<em style=\"font-weight: 400;\">regular-expression</em>参数的方式来过滤显示；</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在分屏显示时，使用&ldquo;/&rdquo;、&ldquo;-&rdquo;或&ldquo;+&rdquo;符号加正则表达式的方式，它将对剩余还未显示的信息使用正则表达式进行过滤显示。其中，&ldquo;/&rdquo;等同关键字<strong>begin</strong>；&ldquo;-&rdquo;等同关键字<strong>exclude</strong>；&ldquo;+&rdquo;等同关键字<strong>include</strong>。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>begin</strong>、<strong>exclude</strong>或<strong>include</strong>关键字的含义如下：</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>begin</strong>：显示特定行及其以后的所有行，该特定行必须包含指定正则表达式。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>exclude</strong>：显示不包含指定正则表达式的所有行。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>include</strong>：只显示包含指定正则表达式的所有行。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">正则表达式（<em style=\"font-weight: 400;\">regular-expression</em>）为1～256个字符的字符串，区分大小写，它还支持多种特殊字符。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>begin</strong>参数应用举例</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#&nbsp;</span>查看当前生效的配置中，从包含&ldquo;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">user-interface</span>&rdquo;字符串的行开始到最后一行的配置信息（该显示信息与用户的当前配置有关）。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">display current-configuration | begin user-interface</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">user-interface aux 0</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">user-interface vty 0 15</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">authentication-mode none</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">user privilege level 3</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">return</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>exclude</strong>参数应用举例</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#&nbsp;</span>查看路由表中的非直连路由（该显示信息与用户的当前配置有关）。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">display ip routing-table | exclude Direct</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Routing Tables: Public</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Destination/Mask&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proto&nbsp; Pre&nbsp; Cost&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; NextHop&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Interface</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1.1.1.0/24&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Static 60&nbsp;&nbsp; 0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 192.168.0.0&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vlan1</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>include</strong>参数应用举例</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 查看路由表中包含Vlan的路由表项（该显示信息与用户的当前配置有关）。</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">display ip routing-table | include Vlan</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Routing Tables: Public</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Destination/Mask&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proto&nbsp; Pre&nbsp; Cost&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; NextHop&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Interface</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">192.168.1.0/24&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Direct 0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 192.168.1.42&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vlan999</p>',52,'1','2020-03-09 16:56:31','2020-03-10 08:52:57',52,67),(95,'电信500M-新和光缆线路','电信500M-新和光缆线路','<p>电信500M 物理线路说明：&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20200301目前：线路为：南山数据机房---16层8楼机房-毛纺-新和小区机房（对接电信出口设备）</p>\n<p>1、将原有的新和机房双纤改为单纤，一芯用于企业新和办公，一芯用于电信500M出口。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;新和至毛纺共8芯目前只全用。</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/ea1e0c8297264ea59348245250104f6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"878\" height=\"658\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/8c7dcede202a41a58084e7721cbbd8c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"996\" height=\"747\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>中间用LC耦合器连接</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/430bf0f32ff74d2694c4104fe4dff0ab.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1019\" height=\"1359\" /></p>\n<p>采用LC-FC与电信尾纤ODF对接</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/c44c08b5fb23472882c086e763ba6431.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"995\" height=\"1327\" /></p>\n<p>对接至电信设备机柜</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/db8ea85034414ef6ba4d7cc757e46b2b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1036\" height=\"1381\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>电信出口核心9306 G1/0/23口</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/3e2757d2f80348d48bdda1a098458834.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>网络信息中心数据机房端口：</p>\n<p>交换机端口：172.16.254.100：G1/0/10,端口从access 改为trunk 以便后期做聚合</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"uploadFile/69699756ca704c569fb504af62be69ab.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"439\" height=\"184\" /></p>',49,'1','2020-03-10 08:36:26','2020-03-10 08:36:26',NULL,122),(96,'通过静态IP接入互联网','通过静态IP接入互联网','<p>通过静态 IP 接入互联网典型配置举例</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>配置静态 IP</li>\n</ol>\n<p># 选择&ldquo;系统 &gt; 配置向导 &gt; 快速接入 Internet&rdquo;，进入配置页面。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;选中路由模式前的单选框，单击&lt;开始配置&gt;按钮，根据当地 ISP 提供的地址，配置 WAN 口参数，</p>\n<p># 快速配置完成后，系统会自动创建一条动态 NAT 策略，无需用户手动配